<rss version="2.0"><channel><title>xkcd.com</title><link>https://xkcd.com/</link><description>xkcd.com: A webcomic of romance and math humor.</description><language>en</language><item><title>Turkish Delight</title><link>https://xkcd.com/1980/</link><description>&lt;img src="https://imgs.xkcd.com/comics/turkish_delight.png" title="I take it Narnia doesn't have Cinnabons? Because if you can magic up a plate of those, I'll betray whoever." alt="I take it Narnia doesn't have Cinnabons? Because if you can magic up a plate of those, I'll betray whoever." /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Apr 2018 04:00:00 -0000</pubDate><guid>https://xkcd.com/1980/</guid></item><item><title>History</title><link>https://xkcd.com/1979/</link><description>&lt;img src="https://imgs.xkcd.com/comics/history.png" title="HISTORIANS: We've decided to trim the past down to make things more manageable. Using BCE/CE, would you rather we lose the odd-numbered or even-numbered years?" alt="HISTORIANS: We've decided to trim the past down to make things more manageable. Using BCE/CE, would you rather we lose the odd-numbered or even-numbered years?" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 11 Apr 2018 04:00:00 -0000</pubDate><guid>https://xkcd.com/1979/</guid></item><item><title>Congressional Testimony</title><link>https://xkcd.com/1978/</link><description>&lt;img src="https://imgs.xkcd.com/comics/congressional_testimony.png" title="James Cameron's Terminator 3 was the REALLY prophetic one. That's why Skynet sent a robot back to the 1990s to prevent him from ever making it, ultimately handing the franchise over to other directors." alt="James Cameron's Terminator 3 was the REALLY prophetic one. That's why Skynet sent a robot back to the 1990s to prevent him from ever making it, ultimately handing the franchise over to other directors." /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Apr 2018 04:00:00 -0000</pubDate><guid>https://xkcd.com/1978/</guid></item><item><title>Paperwork</title><link>https://xkcd.com/1977/</link><description>&lt;img src="https://imgs.xkcd.com/comics/paperwork.png" title="Plus, the photo was geotagged, my unlocked password manager was visible on the laptop, AND you could see my naked reflection in the dark part of the screen." alt="Plus, the photo was geotagged, my unlocked password manager was visible on the laptop, AND you could see my naked reflection in the dark part of the screen." /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Apr 2018 04:00:00 -0000</pubDate><guid>https://xkcd.com/1977/</guid></item></channel></rss>